{"id": 3024, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都有哪些「天气综合征」的初期症状？", "description": "你也有「用天气来指导自己的日常生活方式」的「天气敏感人格」吗？（题图来自：iStock ©️ sesame）", "record_count": 4956, "comment_count": 23, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191010030631hKuUXDTC7elN9YzV.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-11T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5962, "title": "你都有哪些「天气综合征」的初期症状？", "content": "你都有哪些“天气综合征”的初期症状？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 348102, "content": "只有晴天才有心情收拾屋子，哪怕只是多云也不行", "image": "img/option/option/20191010021938q5IY2KLnf9BvN3oE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348103, "content": "天气好的日子，仿佛热爱生活程度都会高一些", "image": "img/option/option/201910100222470WqJbjvnViPcksay.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348104, "content": "下雨/阴天时，更喜欢找一些舒缓/忧郁的歌来听", "image": "img/option/option/20191010022610Mvhz1qEPjxZcWTK2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348105, "content": "看到蓝天白云就控制不住想拍照，还要发条朋友圈", "image": "img/option/option/20191010023323TpAnQGEIfBW250i9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348106, "content": "喜欢用天气来解释各种生活小事，比如某一天的状态", "image": "img/option/option/20191010024341sZDJuQPyWhmkcjUB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348107, "content": "对温度变化特别敏感，每天出门之前必看体感温度", "image": "img/option/option/20191010031351wntzTOCEZedLx4jy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348108, "content": "聊天的开头一定是吐槽天气，“今儿这天实在太差了”", "image": "img/option/option/201910100312296Nf8IkVTg7nxchyd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348109, "content": "每到雾霾天，一定会有“隔窗看天并唉声叹气”的日常环节", "image": "img/option/option/20191010031408dKEe4OLsCHVvl0cF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348110, "content": "还好，我对天气什么的没有那么敏感", "image": "img/option/option/20191010031626dtQFswW31ZuxCIge.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}